(1, '<div style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212); font-family: Consolas, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19px; white-space: pre;\"><h2 style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.3; color: rgb(128, 130, 133); font-size: 1.7em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal;\">Ayurveda</h2><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><font color=\"#4169e1\"><span style=\"outline-color: initial; outline-style: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear;\">Dr Rana’s</span></font>&nbsp;Medical hall is a cult home that use ayurvedic medicine for sexual weakness. Since its inception in 1960, we heal the sexual disorders and diseases with our aged old ayur cure.</p><h2 style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.3; color: rgb(128, 130, 133); font-size: 1.7em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal;\">Ayurveda – The History</h2><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Ayurveda or the Indian system of medicine is perhaps the oldest system of medicine and treatment in the world. We can trace back the history of the principles of Ayurveda to the Indus Valley civilization or even before it. But those medical practices didn’t bare the name Ayurveda.</p><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">It was from the Vedic age, after the advent of Aryans, Ayurveda got its nomenclature and independent status. The Vedic age revolutionized the world culture by the four Vedas, Rig, Yajur, Sama and Adharva. Ayurveda with its concise format is actually the part of the fourth Veda, Adharava. But from the time of the world-famous Vaidya (physician) and a master surgeon, Sushruta, that Ayurveda developed into a vast ocean of medical science.</p><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Charaka, the other end master surgeon and physician supplemented and complemented his contributions. Together they changed the zodiac signs of medical science.</p><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Ayurveda, like&nbsp;<span style=\"outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><font color=\"#4169e1\"><span style=\"outline-color: initial; outline-style: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear;\">Unani</span></font></span>, considers that human body is balanced by humors. These humors are Vata, Pitta and Kapha. The balancing of these three creates the perfect health and imbalance creates ailments. Ayurveda not only treats a particular ailment, but empowers his body and soul in a holistic way to relieve from complete imbalance.</p><figure class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; white-space: normal; outline: none !important;\"><img src=\"https://ranamedicalhall.com/wp-content/themes/ranamedicalhall/assets/img/blog-sidebar/Ayurvedic-treatment-for-Sexual-weakness.jpg\" alt=\"Ayurvedic treatment for Sexual weakness\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; outline: none !important;\"></figure><h2 style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.3; color: rgb(128, 130, 133); font-size: 1.7em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal;\">Ayurveda has 8 branches. They are :</h2><h3 style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(128, 130, 133); font-size: 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal;\">Kayachikitsa (Internal Medicine)</h3><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Agni, – The digestive fire in the body is represented by the word kaya. It is responsible for the metabolism in the body. Moreover, the imbalance of this Agni creates the external and internal havoc in the body. By treating Agni, ayurveda cures fever, diarrhoea, cough etc.</p><h4 style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(128, 130, 133); font-size: 1.3em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal;\">Kaumara-Bhrtya (Pediatrics)</h4><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Kaumara-bhrtya or Bala chikitsa forms an independent part of Ayurveda which deals with the treatment of children.</p><h5 style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(128, 130, 133); font-size: 1.2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal;\">Salakyatantra (ENT)</h5><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">It is the treatment of diseases which affect ears, nose and mouth.</p><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"></p><h6 style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(128, 130, 133); font-size: 1.1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal;\">Salya Tantra (Surgery)</h6><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">It deals with the surgical procedures mentioned in Sushruta Samhita. Thus, different types of surgeries done are cataract, kidney stones, piles and even perforations of the abdomen.</p><h6 style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(128, 130, 133); font-size: 1.1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal;\">Bhuta Vidya (Psychiatry)</h6><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">This branch of Ayurveda executes management and treatment of psychiatric diseases like unmada and apasmara. In addition to the herbal treatments,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ranamedicalhall.com/health-talks//yoga-for-sexual-health-through-unani-medicines/\" style=\"outline: 0px; color: rgb(65, 105, 225); border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; font-weight: 700; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\">yoga</span></a>, pranayama, mantra chikitsa, and special diet are part of it.</p><h6 style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(128, 130, 133); font-size: 1.1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal;\">Vairodh Tantra (Toxicology)</h6><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">It is the branch of Ayurveda which studies and treats the toxins or poisons in the human body</p><h6 style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(128, 130, 133); font-size: 1.1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal;\">Rasayana Tantra (Rejuvenation)</h6><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">The ageing process of human beings curtails by the execution of this chikitsa. A long, healthy rejuvenated life is the product of this treatment. In addition to that, Longevity, memory, complexion, strength of senses are its by-products.</p><h6 style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.7; color: rgb(128, 130, 133); font-size: 1.1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both; white-space: normal;\">Vajikarana Tantra (Aphrodisiacs) (Rejuvenation)</h6><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\">Ayurveda considers sex as one of the pertinent and divine aspects of life. So, this branch is dedicated to sex, treatment of its deceased conditions, infertility problems, enhancement of the reproductive fluid in the body. Ayurvedic medicine for sexual weakness are very safe and effective.</p><h4 style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif