p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;\">Roy Medical Hall is foremost Authentic Unani Medical Centre in India. Our specialities are scientific therapy, Counselling and non-surgical solution for all kinds of male-female Sexual Problems with a Unani system of medication.</p><p style=\"text-align: left; margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;\"><img src=\"https://www.roymedical.com/uploads/trade_mark_roymedical.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"430\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; border: 0px;\"></p>', 0, '2022-09-23 04:31:25', '2022-09-23 04:31:25'),
(14, 'UNDERSTANDING SEXUALITY - SEXOLOGIST DOCTOR', 'Sex is man’s second strongest instinct. An instinct that is second only to the survival instinct. This means that if a man’s life is not immediately imperiled, the next thing he will automatically think of his sex', '<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Many people are confused and bothered by their sexual feelings. Some view sex as something to laugh at or joke about. But throughout history, philosophers, scholars, and religious leaders have thought seriously about sex and its importance to individuals and society. Most religions and cultures have developed moral standards concerning sex.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">The neglect and denial of sexual and reproductive health are the root cause of many health-related problems; Sexuality is a valuable and important component of our well-being; Healthy relationships and personal health are enhanced by familiarity and confidence about our sexuality.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">The World Health Organisation defines sexual health as “a state of physical, emotional, mental and social well-being related to sexuality; it is not merely the absence of disease, dysfunction or infirmity. Sex