x; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">The severity of your problem<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">&nbsp;</strong></strong></span></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">The frequency of sex or ejaculation, etc.</strong></span></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">An Unani physician does not prescribe the strongest drug at the beginning of the treatment. He selects the drug according to the degree of variation from the normal healthy condition and observes the effect produced by the treatment.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">The average time for most people to get full recovery is 2-4 months...</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">The majority of patients who attend our clinics tend to suffer from very long-standing and chronic conditions. In our experience, a short course of medication and treatment isn\'t sometimes sufficient for this type of patient to observe an immediate improvement.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">However, chronic and complicated cases should take the medication for as long as necessary to recover.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: medium; user-select: initial !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">TREATMENT FEE</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">We like to notify you that, buying medication from India or Dubai… The treatment charges are based on different factors i.e. Age, disorder, syndrome, and duration of treatment.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">The charges may vary according to the age factor (For example a 60-year-old person’s treatment cost may go almost 3 and 4 times for the same problem as a 30 years old young man)</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">The cost of medication remains the same as per Indian standard, except that in India we charge Indian rupees and for other countries, the same amount is converted into USD, EURO, GBR, AED &amp; SAR, and the money value stands as per current money exchange rate.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: medium; user-select: initial !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">HOW TO GET MEDICINE FROM US?</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Every day we receive many requests for consultation; every email is read and processed personally by our chief physicians, anyone who wishes to move to non-chemical medication and like to try safe, Kindly fill up the details in the&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline; user-select: initial !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; color: rgb(0, 128, 0);\"><font color=\"#ffffff\"><span style=\"padding: 6px 10px; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; background-color: rgb(93, 177, 21); font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; border-radius: 5px; text-transform: uppercase; user-select: initial !important;\">CONSULTATION FORM</span></font></span></strong></span>&nbsp;and submit it now.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">You will be informed through email about the treatment duration &amp; cost of the medicine and required medicines can be obtained by post or courier after paying the medication cost as mentioned below: -</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underline; font-size: medium; user-select: initial !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">HOW ARE ORDERS SHIPPED?</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Orders are shipped using Indian post-operated standard airmail, speed post, and other globally functional courier services; the final stage of delivery using this system is through each country\'s internal mail system. Delivery times will, therefore, vary depending on the efficiency of the domestic mail system.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: underl