if; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">He is the pioneer in launching a website for promoting Unani. Then, by investing a lot of money, he converted it also into the vernacular language to benefit his large number of patients who are more comfortable with vernacular. The tech-savvy Dr. Roy has played a key role in making the educated youth understand the benefits of Unani.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Yes when it is Unani, it is none other than Dr. Shabeer Ahamed Roy. One can hardly find a person in modern times who has devoted his days and nights for years together to the research and development of Unani and promoting it across the world.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Inspire by the tough changing market conditions he held his principles close to his heart with high esteem.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">He was particular...</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">To understand the patient in as detail as possible.</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">To prepare the herbal medicine formulations in the traditional and authentic way</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">To educate the youth about a system of medicine without any side effects.</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">To use and utilize the advantages of modern communication systems like the internet etc.</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">This relentless effort of Dr. S. A. Roy made him the winner of this coveted international award for the Best Unani Physician at the First International Conference on UNANIPATHY and Complementary Medicine held in Dubai on 11th June 2012.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">His children Dr. Nolifar Roy BAMS, Dr. Niyaz Ahamed Roy BUMS, and Dr. Nishad Roy BUMS are also qualified Unani &amp; Ayurved doctors and closely follow his father’s footsteps in creatively contributing to the promotion of Unani &amp; Ayurved.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">Hakim Ajmal Khan Memorial Society</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">The Hakim Ajmal Khan Memorial Society was founded in 1989 on the grounds of Tibbia College of Ayurvedic &amp; Unani, Karol Bagh, New Delhi. This institution was founded by Late Hakim Ajmal Khan Sahib in 1921 and inaugurated by our Father of the Nation, Mahatma Gandhi. This is the only institution in the world where Ayurvedic &amp; Unani are taught together under one roof.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Late Hakim Ajmal Khan Sahib was an outstanding Physician and Scholar of Unani Medicine. He was an influential figure in the city of Delhi, respected for his aristocratic standing, and behavior, and renowned for miraculous cures. He was a versatile genius of his times, an acclaimed Physician, a statesman of national stature, a poet of great sentiments, a reformer, and an orator.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Hakim Ajmal Khan Memorial Society has a membership of more than five thousand Physicians from Ayurveda, Unani, and other Alternative medicines. The Societys main motto is the promotion of the Indian System of Medicine, especially the Unani and Ayurvedic Systems of Medicine.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Hakim Ajmal Khan Memorial Society from the very beginning takes care of the problems of the Ayurvedic and Unani systems of Medicine and presented many memorandums to the government authorities from time to time. When Students, Teachers, and Doctors of ISM face any problems, the Society represents and takes up their issues with the Government authorities. The Society organizes all seminars and functions in collaboration with other medical organizations and institutions.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">This Organisation is a non-profit organization and does not take any grants from the Government. In 1995 the Society started ALL INDIA HAKIM AJMAL KHAN AWARD in various fields of ISM. The Society\'s Governing body constituted an ALL INDIA HAKIM AJMAL KHAN COMMITTEE under the chairmanship of renowned Unani Physician Prof. M. S. Usmani, Former Vice-chairman of the Minority Commission of India and members of this committee are experts from Ayurveda and Unani.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">The Society\'s Awards were bestowed to acclaimed Ayurvedic and Unani Physicians from India and abroad in the last 10 years. Some of the awardees are:</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; user-select: initial !important;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">Vaidya Nanank Chand Sharma</strong></span></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">Vaidya Devendra</strong></span></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">Dr. Marc Helper</strong></span></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">Dr. Maroof Athique</strong></span></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">Vaidya Kumar Swamiji Maharaj</strong></span></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">Vaidya Pratap Chauhan</strong></span></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">Vaidya Harish Verma</strong></span></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">Hakim Shabeer Ahamed Roy</strong></span></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">In 1995 and 1996 All India Hakim Ajmal Khan Awards were presented by His Excellency Dr. Shanker Dayal Sharma, the then President.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">1997 and 1998 Awards were presented by the Chief Minister of Delhi Mrs. Shiela Dixit.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">1999 and 2000 Awards were presented by Mrs. Najma Heptullah, the then Deputy Speaker of Rajya Sabha and Chairman World Parliament Organization.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">2003, 2004, and 2005 Awards were presented by Dr. Ambumani Ramdoss, the Hon\'ble Health Minister, Govt of India.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">The Award is made \"Global\" in the year 2006 as physicians from other countries are also considered for the award.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0p