: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Moreover don\'t take these medications with nitrate medications, such as...</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">THE HEART DRUGS NITROGLYCERIN (NITRO-BID, OTHERS)</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">ISOSORBIDE MONONITRATE (IMDUR)</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">ISOSORBIDE DINITRATE (ISORDIL)</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">The combination of these medications, which work to widen (dilate) blood vessels, can cause dizziness, low blood pressure, and heart problems such as heart attack or stroke.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb