(20, 'Skin Disorders', 'Symptoms on your skin that appear due to common problems aren&rsquo;t\r\n                always the result of a skin disorder. However, skin problems that have no obvious cause may indicate the\r\n                presence of an actual skin condition that requires treatment. Bowel-related disorders often cause skin\r\n                problems, diabetes experience skin problems...', '<h1 style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px 0px 5px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 22px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(67, 67, 67); border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(1, 116, 0); user-select: initial !important;\"><br></h1><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; user-select: initial !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Symptoms on your skin that appear due to common problems aren’t always the result of a skin disorder. However, skin problems that have no obvious cause may indicate the presence of an actual skin condition that requires treatment.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Bowel-related disorders often cause skin problems, diabetes experience skin problems such as bacterial infections, such as boils, styes, and folliculitis fungal infections, such as athlete’s foot, ringworm, and yeast infections, acanthosis nigricans, diabetic blisters, and diabetic dermopathy.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Stress can cause hormonal imbalances, which may trigger or aggravate skin disorders. Stress-related skin problems eczema, psoriasis, acne, vitiligo, alopecia areata, etc.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">The sun can cause many different skin disorders. Knowing if the sun causes or worsens your skin disorder is important for treating it properly. Some are common and harmless, while others are rare or life-threatening. Sunlight exposure may cause or aggravate moles, wrinkles, sunburn, actinic keratosis skin cancer, etc.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">LEARNING ABOUT PROPER SKINCARE</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Treatment for skin disorders can be very important for skin health. Some conditions require the attention of a doctor, while you can address others safely at home.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">TIPS TO PREVENT INFECTIOUS SKIN DISORDERS</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Wash your hands with soap and warm water frequently.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Avoid sharing eating utensils and drinking glasses with other people.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Avoid direct contact with the skin of other people who have an infection.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Avoid environmental and dietary allergens.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Avoid contact with harsh chemicals or other irritants.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Clean things in public spaces, such as gym equipment, before using them.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Don’t share personal items, such as blankets, hairbrushes, or swimsuits.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Sleep for at least seven hours each night.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Drink plenty of water.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Avoid excessive physical or emotional stress.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Eat a nutritious and healthy diet.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Protect your skin from excessive cold, heat, and wind.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Get vaccinated for infectious skin conditions, such as chickenpox.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important;\">WHAT IS THE CURE?</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Naturally, beautiful skin is clean, soft, and supple, just like a child\'s skin. It glows naturally and is spotless. Skin Problems are generally caused by impurities in the blood. Most remedies act externally and provide only transitory relief and do not address the root cause.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 8px; padding: 0px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify; user-select: initial !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: initial !important; font-size: medium;\">Unani medication mainly works on blood purification, cures constipation, corrects indigestion, and increases natural immunity to improve the overall health of skin condition &amp; complexion.</span></p><h1 style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 20px; line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); user-select: initial !important;\">Quick Links</h1>', '1663910010.jpg', 1, 0, '2022-09-22 23:43:30', '2022-09-23 01:50:26');
