yle=\"outline-color: initial; outline-style: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear;\">Venereal treatment</span></font>s(STD) etc.</p><h2 style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.3; color: rgb(128, 130, 133); font-size: 1.7em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both;\">Unani</h2><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">A student of Unani can experience the status of it, if he observes the travelling of this cult system across the globe, spanning over different cultures, over different periods. Presumably, four time periods in four distinct geographical belts developed this system.<br style=\"outline: none !important;\">1.Greek period<br style=\"outline: none !important;\">2.Arab-Persian period<br style=\"outline: none !important;\">3.Spanish period<br style=\"outline: none !important;\">4.Indian period</p><h4 style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(128, 130, 133); font-size: 1.3em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both;\">The Canon of medicine</h4><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">Based on the teachings of the Greek physicians Hippocrates and Galen, Ibn –e-Sina conceived the hypothetical formulations of the Unani systemin in his classical 11th-century work, The Canon of medicine’.</p><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">From there, this Hellenistic system of medicine gained tremendous momentum in the Arabian Peninsula. And Unani attained its present status, shape and size, furthermore.</p><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">On the other hand, the propagation of the divine healing of cupping therapy (Hijamath), by Islam, revolutionized the unani system, which transmitted to the nook and corner of the world. Unani reached India easily because of Delhi Sultanate..</p><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">History says that, in 1360 AD, King Allauddin Khalji’s palace was a dome of a number of Hakims, with a very high Unani expertise. But, on the Mughal period, Unani system of medicine attained its pinnacle of glory.</p><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\"></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; outline: none !important;\"><img src=\"https://ranamedicalhall.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Authentic-unani-sex-Medicine-1.jpg\" alt=\"Authentic Unani Sex Medicine\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; outline: none !important;\"></figure><h4 style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Rubik, sans-serif; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(128, 130, 133); font-size: 1.3em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; clear: both;\">The Mughal period</h4><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\"></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">In effect, In India, the Unani system attained a new turn with the vehement influence of the classic Indian system of medicine –The Ayurveda. Even though, Unani had a marked hypothetical resemblance with Ayurveda already, after its advent to India, it embraced the visionary medical fundamentals of the promulgators of Ayurveda, Sushruta and Charaka.</p><p style=\"outline: 0px; word-break: break-word; margin-bottom: 1.75em; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(94, 98, 113); font-family: Rubik, sans-serif;\">In effect, a basic Indian transgressed in an&nbsp;<